1
00:00:09,314 --> 00:00:11,029
Untuk Thorfun.

2
00:00:11,368 --> 00:00:12,751
Phoon dah sampai di Chiang Mai.

3
00:00:13,177 --> 00:00:14,965
Hari ini, Phoon terserempak P'Fah juga.

4
00:00:15,205 --> 00:00:16,684
Dan Phoon menipu,

5
00:00:17,210 --> 00:00:18,577
kata Fun baik-baik saja.

6
00:00:21,401 --> 00:00:23,103
Nak tidur di bilik P'Fah malam ini?

7
00:00:23,866 --> 00:00:26,197
Awak teman saya sampai saya tidur, ya?

8
00:00:26,877 --> 00:00:27,665
Ya.

9
00:00:28,299 --> 00:00:29,441
Err, Phoon.

10
00:00:29,594 --> 00:00:31,392
Boleh saya minta LINE ID Fun?

11
00:00:31,920 --> 00:00:36,164
Awak tengah bercinta dengan sesiapa?

12
00:00:36,237 --> 00:00:37,505
Saya tak bercinta dengan sesiapa.

13
00:00:37,739 --> 00:00:40,659
Saya tak mampu jadi langit untuk sesiapa.

14
00:01:42,220 --> 00:01:43,790
Boleh awak jadi langit untuk saya?

15
00:01:45,000 --> 00:01:46,190
Tak boleh ke?

16
00:02:01,170 --> 00:02:01,930
Phoon.

17
00:02:02,510 --> 00:02:04,050
Phoon. Phoon.

18
00:02:05,160 --> 00:02:06,030
Ya?

19
00:02:06,070 --> 00:02:08,430
Awak okey? Tiba-tiba diam.

20
00:02:09,140 --> 00:02:09,990
Oh.

21
00:02:10,990 --> 00:02:11,810
Saya okey.

22
00:02:13,040 --> 00:02:14,650
Saya ingat awak bosan dengar Fah cakap.

23
00:02:19,010 --> 00:02:22,380
Macam nak hujan. Kita balik?

24
00:02:23,600 --> 00:02:24,180
Jom.

25
00:02:51,320 --> 00:02:52,910
Hei, Jo. Ke mana tadi?

26
00:02:53,170 --> 00:02:54,760
Buat urusan sikit. Awak pula?

27
00:02:59,730 --> 00:03:00,910
Keluar.

28
00:03:03,790 --> 00:03:06,190
Tak pakai baju hujan. Nanti selsema.

29
00:03:06,750 --> 00:03:07,650
Saya okey.

30
00:03:07,690 --> 00:03:08,920
Lepas ni nak ke mana?

31
00:03:09,400 --> 00:03:10,400
Balik ke kondo saya.

32
00:03:10,660 --> 00:03:11,950
Dan sial, hujan lagi.

33
00:03:12,520 --> 00:03:13,320
Awak pula?

34
00:03:13,810 --> 00:03:15,280
Saya balik juga.

35
00:03:15,700 --> 00:03:17,620
- Pandu hati-hati.
- Awak juga.

36
00:03:17,920 --> 00:03:19,320
- Jumpa lagi.
- Bye.

37
00:03:27,230 --> 00:03:28,380
Itu kawan awak?

38
00:03:30,630 --> 00:03:31,270
Ya.

39
00:03:33,350 --> 00:03:34,470
Nama dia siapa?

40
00:03:35,690 --> 00:03:37,390
Nama dia Johan.

41
00:03:38,180 --> 00:03:40,040
Oh, P'Johan.

42
00:03:41,900 --> 00:03:42,690
Kenapa?

43
00:03:42,940 --> 00:03:43,780
Berminat?

44
00:03:45,320 --> 00:03:46,100
Tak.

45
00:03:47,230 --> 00:03:48,890
Kalau saya nak cadangkan seseorang,

46
00:03:49,120 --> 00:03:52,560
Jo orang terakhir saya akan cadangkan.

47
00:03:53,380 --> 00:03:55,360
Tak—kedua terakhir.

48
00:03:55,690 --> 00:03:56,670
Yang terakhir, Arthit.

49
00:03:59,200 --> 00:04:01,080
Hmm. Kenapa pula?

50
00:04:01,530 --> 00:04:04,450
Dia bukan orang yang baik.

51
00:04:08,550 --> 00:04:10,100
Kalau dari kumpulan tu saya nak cadangkan,

52
00:04:11,150 --> 00:04:13,200
saya paling nak awak jumpa Hill.

53
00:04:13,880 --> 00:04:17,260
Kenapa awak rasa perlu kenalkan orang pada saya?

54
00:04:17,840 --> 00:04:20,810
Saya cuma rasa elok kalau ada orang jaga awak.

55
00:04:21,330 --> 00:04:26,620
Kalau ada, biarlah orang yang baik dan boleh dipercayai.

56
00:04:34,020 --> 00:04:36,620
Jadi kalau awak bercinta, kena lulus Thorfun dulu, ya?

57
00:04:41,150 --> 00:04:41,900
Ya.

58
00:04:42,910 --> 00:04:45,560
Lepas tu kena lulus saya juga.

59
00:04:46,130 --> 00:04:47,890
Saya abang awak, kan.

60
00:05:20,520 --> 00:05:22,100
Macam bekalan elektrik nak terputus lagi.

61
00:05:23,550 --> 00:05:24,660
Awak okey?

62
00:05:25,780 --> 00:05:26,930
Err...

63
00:05:27,600 --> 00:05:29,750
Sejujurnya...

64
00:05:30,250 --> 00:05:32,170
Nak tidur di bilik P'Fah malam ini?

65
00:05:38,380 --> 00:05:39,110
Ya.

66
00:06:01,160 --> 00:06:03,210
Maaf menyusahkan awak lagi.

67
00:06:03,650 --> 00:06:04,780
Tak apa.

68
00:06:10,460 --> 00:06:12,070
Saya baru pesan ini.

69
00:06:14,170 --> 00:06:15,550
Boleh saya duduk sini?

70
00:06:16,090 --> 00:06:16,780
Boleh.

71
00:06:26,930 --> 00:06:27,600
Ini air.

72
00:06:36,550 --> 00:06:39,740
Saya rasa lebih baik awak pindah asrama.

73
00:06:41,820 --> 00:06:44,210
Saya carikan tempat baru untuk awak.

74
00:06:50,270 --> 00:06:52,110
Ayah saya mungkin marah.

75
00:06:52,480 --> 00:06:54,140
Dia dah bayar deposit.

76
00:06:55,240 --> 00:06:57,960
Kalau begitu, saya cakap dengan ayah awak sendiri.

77
00:06:58,230 --> 00:06:59,430
Boleh saya minta nombor ayah awak?

78
00:07:13,860 --> 00:07:16,640
Saya dah hantar nombor ayah saya.

79
00:07:21,020 --> 00:07:24,290
Tunggu sekejap. Saya cakap dengan ayah awak.

80
00:07:38,190 --> 00:07:39,540
Awak belum tidur lagi?

81
00:07:43,800 --> 00:07:45,990
Kalau begitu, saya tidur dulu.

82
00:07:46,120 --> 00:07:46,800
Mm.

83
00:07:56,590 --> 00:07:57,280
Siapa tu?

84
00:08:00,820 --> 00:08:01,540
Helo?

85
00:08:01,760 --> 00:08:03,840
Helo, Pak Cik. Ini Tonfah.

86
00:08:05,790 --> 00:08:07,520
Oh, Tonfah?

87
00:08:08,020 --> 00:08:09,700
Terkejut saya. Saya tertanya siapa tadi.

88
00:08:10,190 --> 00:08:15,610
Kenapa telefon? Ada apa-apa ke?

89
00:08:16,490 --> 00:08:18,980
Pasal Phoon.

90
00:08:20,270 --> 00:08:21,180
Pasal Phoon?

91
00:08:22,190 --> 00:08:23,120
Kenapa?

92
00:08:24,730 --> 00:08:26,750
Tentang asrama yang Pak Cik pilih untuk Phoon.

93
00:08:27,500 --> 00:08:30,980
Keadaannya tak begitu baik.

94
00:08:31,600 --> 00:08:33,990
Jadi saya rasa lebih baik dia pindah.

95
00:08:34,140 --> 00:08:36,350
Tapi saya nak minta izin Pak Cik dulu.

96
00:08:36,830 --> 00:08:39,980
Saya tak sangka asrama tu tak elok.

97
00:08:40,030 --> 00:08:42,750
Saya baru tukar kerja dan sangat sibuk.

98
00:08:42,900 --> 00:08:45,770
Jadi saya suruh setiausaha uruskan tempahan.

99
00:08:46,370 --> 00:08:48,070
Faham.

100
00:08:48,600 --> 00:08:49,390
Baiklah.

101
00:08:50,170 --> 00:08:51,800
Tonfah belajar di sini juga?

102
00:08:52,010 --> 00:08:53,050
Saya tak tahu pun.

103
00:08:53,540 --> 00:08:56,480
Ya, saya belajar sini, dan terserempak Typhoon.

104
00:08:56,730 --> 00:09:00,250
Apa? Awak terserempak Typhoon juga?

105
00:09:00,310 --> 00:09:02,910
Macam mana dia?

106
00:09:03,320 --> 00:09:06,290
Dia ada cakap apa-apa pada awak?

107
00:09:09,490 --> 00:09:10,610
Dia tak cakap apa-apa.

108
00:09:11,780 --> 00:09:15,390
Dia ada sebut Thorfun tak?

109
00:09:16,820 --> 00:09:19,140
Saya dengar dia belajar perubatan dekat rumah, ya?

110
00:09:21,500 --> 00:09:23,520
Kalau begitu, saya akan uruskan Typhoon sendiri.

111
00:09:23,960 --> 00:09:25,240
Termasuk carikan asrama baru.

112
00:09:25,440 --> 00:09:28,490
Kalau begitu, saya serahkan Typhoon pada awak.

113
00:09:29,210 --> 00:09:31,090
Ya, Pak Cik. Jangan risau.

114
00:09:40,180 --> 00:09:41,180
Awak okey?

115
00:09:41,900 --> 00:09:43,560
Kita pergi cari asrama baru sama-sama.

116
00:09:44,570 --> 00:09:45,930
Ayah benarkan?

117
00:09:46,680 --> 00:09:47,330
Ya.

118
00:09:59,250 --> 00:10:00,440
P'Fah.

119
00:10:00,690 --> 00:10:02,060
Ada apa-apa?

120
00:10:03,840 --> 00:10:04,660
Tak ada.

121
00:10:05,120 --> 00:10:06,860
Awak patut pergi mandi.

122
00:10:07,140 --> 00:10:09,330
Awak penat seharian. Rehatlah.

123
00:10:20,040 --> 00:10:23,390
Typhoon ada sebut Thorfun tak?

124
00:10:31,450 --> 00:10:33,320
Fun, awak di mana?

125
00:10:52,480 --> 00:10:55,470
Esok pagi saya jemput awak. Rith nak cakap dengan awak.

126
00:11:08,500 --> 00:11:10,590
Awak pasti tak nak P'Fah hantar awak?

127
00:11:11,710 --> 00:11:12,610
Saya pasti.

128
00:11:12,770 --> 00:11:13,950
Pak Cik kata dia akan datang jemput saya.

129
00:11:14,670 --> 00:11:16,660
Tiba-tiba mereka terbang ke Chiang Mai macam ni.

130
00:11:17,050 --> 00:11:18,160
Ada apa-apa ke?

131
00:11:18,840 --> 00:11:21,000
Pasal P'Fah telefon malam tadi ke?

132
00:11:23,910 --> 00:11:25,110
Saya tak tahu.

133
00:11:25,830 --> 00:11:26,880
Saya gerak dulu.

134
00:11:27,780 --> 00:11:28,440
Okey.

135
00:12:07,750 --> 00:12:10,540
Kenapa tiba-tiba datang ke Chiang Mai?

136
00:12:11,970 --> 00:12:13,980
Rith memang ada urusan dengan klien di sini.

137
00:12:14,980 --> 00:12:18,290
Tapi malam tadi tiba-tiba dipercepatkan ke hari ini.

138
00:12:20,720 --> 00:12:22,020
Pasal P'Fah, kan?

139
00:12:24,110 --> 00:12:25,490
Mungkin.

140
00:12:26,820 --> 00:12:27,900
Ayah marah?

141
00:12:29,520 --> 00:12:32,780
Saya dah pesan jangan terlibat dengan Tonfah.

142
00:12:33,230 --> 00:12:36,550
Kalau keluarga Tonfah tahu pasal cerainya,

143
00:12:36,970 --> 00:12:40,820
sebab ibu Thorfun tangkap dia dengan perempuan lain,

144
00:12:41,770 --> 00:12:43,260
dan tahu awak anak dia—

145
00:12:49,680 --> 00:12:50,550
Anak luar nikah.

146
00:12:52,870 --> 00:12:53,690
Betul.

147
00:12:53,980 --> 00:12:55,500
Sebab itu dia tak berani berdepan mereka.

148
00:12:55,780 --> 00:12:57,570
Dah bertahun dia tak hubungi keluarga itu.

149
00:12:58,180 --> 00:12:59,320
Tapi—

150
00:13:00,760 --> 00:13:03,010
Ibu bapa P’Fah bukan macam tu.

151
00:13:03,800 --> 00:13:04,910
Aku tahu.

152
00:13:05,780 --> 00:13:08,310
Tapi Typhoon patut kenal ayah dia.

153
00:13:09,180 --> 00:13:12,780
Rith sangat hormat ibu bapa Tonfah.

154
00:13:13,090 --> 00:13:14,990
Dia takut dipandang buruk.

155
00:13:15,590 --> 00:13:18,430
Dan ia mungkin jejaskan kerjaya dia.

156
00:13:19,180 --> 00:13:20,540
Kau kena faham dia.

157
00:13:24,040 --> 00:13:24,770
Aku faham.

158
00:13:26,120 --> 00:13:27,730
Kau memang budak baik.

159
00:13:28,960 --> 00:13:31,060
Walau lepas semua yang dia buat pada kau,

160
00:13:31,730 --> 00:13:34,880
kau masih sayang dan hormat dia sebagai ayah.

161
00:13:37,740 --> 00:13:40,370
Dia satu-satunya keluarga yang aku ada.

162
00:14:12,540 --> 00:14:13,370
Typhoon.

163
00:14:14,070 --> 00:14:16,170
Kau dah tahu Tonfah belajar sini, kan?

164
00:14:18,050 --> 00:14:18,820
Ya.

165
00:14:20,200 --> 00:14:22,640
Tapi aku tak sangka jumpa dia secepat ini.

166
00:14:23,370 --> 00:14:24,970
Apa kau cakap pada dia?

167
00:14:27,470 --> 00:14:28,830
Aku tak cakap apa-apa.

168
00:14:33,810 --> 00:14:35,370
Apa sebenarnya kau nak?

169
00:14:35,590 --> 00:14:37,990
Bunuh anak aku belum cukup untuk kau?

170
00:14:38,530 --> 00:14:41,020
Kau sampai buat Wit dan Pha pandang aku buruk.

171
00:14:41,260 --> 00:14:42,700
Aku dah cakap, kan?

172
00:14:42,880 --> 00:14:44,750
Kau boleh belajar di mana saja,

173
00:14:45,080 --> 00:14:46,570
tapi jauhkan diri daripada Tonfah.

174
00:14:46,630 --> 00:14:47,720
Faham?

175
00:14:48,770 --> 00:14:52,380
Atau kau nak beritahu Tonfah pasal Thorfun?

176
00:14:52,650 --> 00:14:55,210
Yang kau bunuh kakak kau sendiri?

177
00:14:55,730 --> 00:14:58,100
Mesti dia bangga sangat dengan kau.

178
00:14:59,970 --> 00:15:01,450
Aku tak bunuh Fun.

179
00:15:02,140 --> 00:15:03,380
Aku tak sengaja.

180
00:15:03,530 --> 00:15:05,100
Jadi kau kata kau tak bersalah?

181
00:15:05,280 --> 00:15:08,340
Tengok apa yang jadi pada aku.

182
00:15:08,730 --> 00:15:10,890
Semua dah hancur.

183
00:15:11,130 --> 00:15:15,790
Keluarga aku berpecah.
Dan kau kata kau tak buat salah?

184
00:15:17,360 --> 00:15:20,490
Ingat ini—tak ada siapa nak kau.

185
00:15:20,880 --> 00:15:23,120
Aku pun tak pernah nak kau lahir.

186
00:15:23,790 --> 00:15:26,330
Kau tahu mak kau tinggalkan kau masa kecil?

187
00:15:26,460 --> 00:15:28,860
Dan sekarang tak ada siapa tahu dia di mana.

188
00:15:29,340 --> 00:15:31,030
Kalau bukan sebab ibu Thorfun,

189
00:15:31,360 --> 00:15:36,710
kau takkan berdiri di sini pun.
Tengok macam mana kau balas kami.

190
00:15:36,850 --> 00:15:38,870
Kau bunuh anak kami.

191
00:15:41,990 --> 00:15:43,750
Dan ingat betul-betul—

192
00:15:44,070 --> 00:15:48,530
tak ada yang anggap kau keluarga selain Thorfun dan Tonfah.

193
00:15:50,430 --> 00:15:51,890
Bila Thorfun dah mati,

194
00:15:52,550 --> 00:15:54,720
kau merangkak balik pada Tonfah,

195
00:15:55,530 --> 00:15:57,560
ingat dia takkan buang kau, kan?

196
00:15:59,090 --> 00:16:01,980
Ayah, boleh aku tinggal dengan P’Fah?

197
00:16:02,610 --> 00:16:04,910
Aku takkan cakap apa-apa. Aku janji.

198
00:16:05,220 --> 00:16:07,720
Ya, kau kena janji.

199
00:16:08,680 --> 00:16:10,400
Sebab kalau kau beritahu dia,

200
00:16:11,170 --> 00:16:12,850
dia tetap akan buang kau.

201
00:16:13,240 --> 00:16:15,840
Sebab kau takut dia benci kau, kan?

202
00:16:16,220 --> 00:16:17,440
Kan?

203
00:16:21,450 --> 00:16:24,580
Kau kena tarik diri dari universiti minggu ini.

204
00:16:29,140 --> 00:16:30,410
Ayah.

205
00:16:31,100 --> 00:16:33,480
Ayah dah jual rumah di Phuket.

206
00:16:33,840 --> 00:16:36,140
Kalau aku tarik diri juga, aku nak pergi mana?

207
00:16:37,120 --> 00:16:39,820
Kau nak pergi mana, itu masalah kau. Aku tak peduli.

208
00:16:40,400 --> 00:16:44,320
Tapi kau mesti jauhkan diri dari keluarga Tonfah.

209
00:16:44,480 --> 00:16:46,030
Lagi jauh, lagi bagus.

210
00:16:46,330 --> 00:16:49,400
Pasal duit, aku suruh Kong uruskan.

211
00:16:50,110 --> 00:16:51,180
Ingat ini.

212
00:16:52,100 --> 00:16:53,680
Jangan bagi aku nampak muka kau lagi.

213
00:16:54,220 --> 00:16:55,460
Faham?

214
00:17:02,190 --> 00:17:04,260
Ayah, tolong jangan.

215
00:17:04,730 --> 00:17:06,690
Tolong jangan tinggalkan aku.

216
00:17:06,710 --> 00:17:08,930
Maafkan aku.

217
00:17:09,710 --> 00:17:11,220
Aku salah.

218
00:17:12,230 --> 00:17:15,710
Apa pun, itu salah aku.

219
00:17:16,560 --> 00:17:18,410
Aku saja yang bersalah.

220
00:17:20,950 --> 00:17:23,640
Aku tak nak lahir semata-mata nak rosakkan hidup ayah.

221
00:17:24,630 --> 00:17:29,650
Aku akan diam, tapi tolong...
jangan tinggalkan aku.

222
00:17:30,860 --> 00:17:32,700
Kalau kau masih anggap aku ayah kau,

223
00:17:33,240 --> 00:17:35,280
kau mesti berhenti campur hal dengan Tonfah.

224
00:18:27,810 --> 00:18:29,010
P’Fah.

225
00:18:39,860 --> 00:18:41,610
Ya, P’Fah?

226
00:18:42,860 --> 00:18:44,590
Kau tak balas, jadi aku telefon.

227
00:18:44,770 --> 00:18:46,010
Kau masih dengan ayah kau?

228
00:18:48,300 --> 00:18:49,220
Tak.

229
00:18:50,120 --> 00:18:51,460
Aku baru balik bilik.

230
00:18:55,780 --> 00:18:56,940
P’Fah.

231
00:18:57,250 --> 00:18:57,940
Ya?

232
00:19:01,190 --> 00:19:04,060
Kau lapang kebelakangan ni?

233
00:19:05,290 --> 00:19:07,930
Ya, aku lapang.

234
00:19:08,050 --> 00:19:09,110
Kenapa?

235
00:19:12,790 --> 00:19:14,460
Boleh bawa aku keluar pergi mana-mana?

236
00:19:15,830 --> 00:19:16,740
Tolong?

237
00:19:19,010 --> 00:19:21,700
Aku betul-betul nak keluar dengan kau.

238
00:19:23,250 --> 00:19:25,380
Boleh. Kau nak pergi mana?

239
00:19:32,440 --> 00:19:33,660
Mana-mana pun.

240
00:19:35,850 --> 00:19:37,270
Asalkan kau ada dengan aku.

241
00:19:38,630 --> 00:19:41,090
Aku nak pergi mana-mana dengan kau.

242
00:19:44,920 --> 00:19:46,820
Kau okey?

243
00:19:47,210 --> 00:19:48,660
Ayah kau cakap apa?

244
00:19:49,840 --> 00:19:51,680
Ayah cuma datang sebab kerja.

245
00:19:53,540 --> 00:19:54,770
Jadi dia singgah jumpa aku.

246
00:19:56,450 --> 00:19:57,300
Faham.

247
00:19:59,840 --> 00:20:00,430
Er...

248
00:20:01,030 --> 00:20:02,600
Aku letak dulu, P’Fah.

249
