251
00:20:29,900 --> 00:20:31,820
Kenapa kau yang pergi?

252
00:20:33,230 --> 00:20:34,870
Kenapa aku yang ditinggalkan?

253
00:20:36,590 --> 00:20:39,250
Kenapa bukan aku saja?

254
00:21:28,470 --> 00:21:29,270
Typhoon.

255
00:21:31,920 --> 00:21:33,360
Kau okey?

256
00:21:36,200 --> 00:21:37,650
Tak apa.

257
00:21:39,580 --> 00:21:43,090
Aku rasa ayah mungkin tertekan pasal kerja.

258
00:21:44,030 --> 00:21:46,150
Jadi dia mungkin hilang sabar.

259
00:21:46,390 --> 00:21:47,830
Kalau gagal peperiksaan ini—

260
00:21:48,410 --> 00:21:49,470
tak apa.

261
00:21:50,640 --> 00:21:51,960
Kau boleh ulang ambil lain kali.

262
00:21:52,640 --> 00:21:54,150
Boleh tak berhenti cakap macam tu?

263
00:21:56,220 --> 00:21:58,600
Macam mana kau boleh kata tak apa?

264
00:21:59,420 --> 00:22:00,800
Kau takkan faham aku.

265
00:22:02,470 --> 00:22:04,080
Semua orang sayang kau.

266
00:22:05,370 --> 00:22:07,250
Aku ni cuma pembawa malang.

267
00:22:08,170 --> 00:22:10,950
Apa pun aku buat, tetap tak cukup bagus.

268
00:22:13,040 --> 00:22:15,020
Rumah ni pun tak perlukan aku.

269
00:22:15,160 --> 00:22:20,470
Jangan cakap macam tu.
Kau nak aku buat apa untuk kau?

270
00:22:25,700 --> 00:22:27,290
Tak ada apa yang kau boleh buat untuk aku.

271
00:22:31,250 --> 00:22:32,130
Typhoon.

272
00:22:40,440 --> 00:22:41,460
Kau pergi lagi?

273
00:22:41,660 --> 00:22:42,790
Tak boleh kau tinggal?

274
00:22:43,300 --> 00:22:44,360
Jangan telefon untuk kejar aku.

275
00:22:44,950 --> 00:22:46,110
Pergi.

276
00:23:18,352 --> 00:23:19,500
Aku akan balik.

277
00:23:26,510 --> 00:23:27,310
Typhoon.

278
00:23:27,740 --> 00:23:28,560
Kau dekat mana?

279
00:23:29,040 --> 00:23:30,530
Kenapa bising sangat?

280
00:23:32,050 --> 00:23:33,330
Aku dah cakap jangan telefon.

281
00:23:33,880 --> 00:23:35,520
Jom balik, okey?

282
00:23:35,640 --> 00:23:36,460
Aku tak nak balik.

283
00:23:37,450 --> 00:23:39,680
Tak boleh kita cakap elok-elok?

284
00:23:40,140 --> 00:23:41,970
Tak ada apa nak dibincang, sial.

285
00:23:42,750 --> 00:23:44,930
Berhenti telefon aku. Kau menyusahkan.

286
00:23:45,310 --> 00:23:46,100
Typhoon.

287
00:24:00,610 --> 00:24:01,450
Hei!

288
00:24:07,190 --> 00:24:08,530
Kau baru langgar aku.

289
00:24:10,420 --> 00:24:11,470
Hei!

290
00:24:16,560 --> 00:24:17,640
Apa benda ni?

291
00:24:21,840 --> 00:24:23,930
Berhenti telefon dah!

292
00:24:28,210 --> 00:24:30,560
Typhoon, apa jadi?

293
00:24:31,010 --> 00:24:32,320
Kau okey?

294
00:24:33,370 --> 00:24:34,410
Helo, Typhoon.

295
00:24:34,620 --> 00:24:37,440
Tunggu situ. Aku datang.

296
00:24:56,630 --> 00:24:58,120
Masih muda lagi.

297
00:24:58,250 --> 00:24:59,260
Sayangnya.

298
00:24:59,670 --> 00:25:01,280
Budak baik, nombor satu kelas.

299
00:25:01,380 --> 00:25:03,710
Banyak potensi. Ruginya.

300
00:25:04,310 --> 00:25:05,880
Aku dengar dia keluar malam-malam.

301
00:25:06,620 --> 00:25:08,710
Lepas tu pemandu mabuk lawan arus.

302
00:25:08,950 --> 00:25:11,120
- Wah.
- Dia mati di tempat kejadian.

303
00:25:11,500 --> 00:25:12,700
Kesian betul.

304
00:25:13,520 --> 00:25:16,910
Kenapa dia bawa kereta lewat malam?

305
00:25:17,980 --> 00:25:22,480
Katanya adik dia bergaduh di bar.

306
00:25:22,960 --> 00:25:25,570
Dia risau, jadi dia cepat-cepat cari dia.

307
00:25:25,870 --> 00:25:29,120
Malang betul ada adik macam tu.

308
00:25:29,510 --> 00:25:31,730
Muda-muda dah masuk bar.

309
00:25:32,150 --> 00:25:36,950
Dia pun tak belajar.
Kakak yang dia harap pun pergi dulu.

310
00:25:37,360 --> 00:25:38,070
Mm.

311
00:25:38,290 --> 00:25:41,800
Aku dengar mak ayah dia bergaduh pasal tu.

312
00:25:42,270 --> 00:25:46,260
Tak ada siapa nak jaga adik tu.

313
00:25:46,840 --> 00:25:49,450
- Betul ke?
- Ya, itu yang aku dengar.

314
00:25:52,440 --> 00:25:54,810
Budak tak guna! Budak sial!

315
00:25:54,980 --> 00:25:57,930
Kau buat anak aku mati!

316
00:25:58,220 --> 00:26:00,290
Kau bunuh anak aku!

317
00:26:09,890 --> 00:26:10,850
Maaf.

318
00:26:14,010 --> 00:26:18,100
Budak sial, ingat ni—kau tak patut jadi anak aku.

319
00:26:19,850 --> 00:26:21,260
Kau nak pergi mana? Tunggu!

320
00:26:24,510 --> 00:26:29,270
Lepas tu, keluarga kami berpecah.

321
00:26:30,850 --> 00:26:33,970
Hancur sampai tak boleh dibaiki lagi.

322
00:26:37,170 --> 00:26:39,660
Cukup. Aku takkan tahan kau lagi.

323
00:26:39,840 --> 00:26:41,800
Kenapa? Aku buat apa?

324
00:26:42,040 --> 00:26:45,330
Kau kaki perempuan, tidur dengan sesiapa saja.

325
00:26:45,520 --> 00:26:49,330
Dah kahwin aku pun, kau buat perempuan lain mengandung.

326
00:26:49,620 --> 00:26:51,090
Diam. Berhenti cakap.

327
00:26:51,520 --> 00:26:54,830
Kau tahu aku tahan besarkan budak tu lebih 10 tahun?

328
00:26:54,980 --> 00:26:56,150
Itu dah lebih dari cukup.

329
00:26:56,300 --> 00:27:03,320
Setiap kali aku tengok muka dia, aku nampak
keluarga kita hancur. Kau tahu tak?

330
00:27:03,330 --> 00:27:05,870
Aku dah cakap, aku tak sengaja buat dia mengandung.

331
00:27:06,120 --> 00:27:10,490
Dia anak luar nikah, dan dia punca anak aku mati.

332
00:27:11,090 --> 00:27:13,520
Kenapa bukan budak tu yang mati?

333
00:27:14,310 --> 00:27:15,710
Kenapa mesti Fun?

334
00:27:16,450 --> 00:27:18,880
Kenapa mesti anak aku?

335
00:27:19,650 --> 00:27:21,480
Masih menangis macam biasa.

336
00:27:29,890 --> 00:27:30,560
Fun.

337
00:27:39,090 --> 00:27:40,690
Aku rindu kau selama ni.

338
00:27:42,210 --> 00:27:43,490
Aku tahu.

339
00:27:44,370 --> 00:27:46,420
Kau tulis pada aku setiap hari.

340
00:27:52,310 --> 00:27:54,570
Aku pun rindu kau.

341
00:28:02,560 --> 00:28:06,080
Kau dah lalui banyak benda teruk, kan?

342
00:28:09,670 --> 00:28:11,190
Maaf.

343
00:28:12,390 --> 00:28:14,470
Maaf sebab aku tak ada dengan kau.

344
00:28:17,800 --> 00:28:22,330
Aku pun minta maaf. Maaf... maaf, Fun.

345
00:28:26,140 --> 00:28:28,340
Semua ni bukan salah kau.

346
00:28:43,110 --> 00:28:45,100
Jangan bergantung pada aku lagi.

347
00:28:46,130 --> 00:28:48,140
Kau kena teruskan hidup.

348
00:28:49,640 --> 00:28:50,890
Faham?

349
00:28:54,160 --> 00:28:55,650
Tolong sayang diri sendiri.

350
00:28:57,250 --> 00:28:59,740
Macam aku sayang kau, okey?

351
00:29:02,410 --> 00:29:03,810
Boleh tak...

352
00:29:06,130 --> 00:29:08,240
