421
00:35:25,700 --> 00:35:28,390
Kau selalu panggil diri macam tu?

422
00:35:28,970 --> 00:35:31,320
Aku buat macam tu dengan kau je, Phoon.

423
00:35:32,810 --> 00:35:34,560
Kau ingat kenapa?

424
00:35:38,720 --> 00:35:39,800
Masa kita kecil dulu—

425
00:35:40,190 --> 00:35:41,970
Ramai budak di kawasan kita.

426
00:35:42,420 --> 00:35:44,080
Kalau aku cuma panggil diri “P’,”

427
00:35:44,480 --> 00:35:46,080
