428
00:35:46,170 --> 00:35:48,090
Jadi aku guna nama aku.

429
00:35:48,370 --> 00:35:49,570
Supaya kau tahu.

430
00:35:49,950 --> 00:35:51,040
Oh.

431
00:36:11,500 --> 00:36:13,800
Terima kasih tolong aku pindah asrama.

432
00:36:15,190 --> 00:36:18,590
Sejujurnya, terima kasih untuk semuanya.

433
00:36:19,810 --> 00:36:21,260
Tak ada apa pun.

434
00:36:26,080 --> 00:36:29,430
Aku kena pergi. Aku nak tuisyen pelajar junior.

435
00:36:31,080 --> 00:36:32,130
Okey.

436
00:36:33,190 --> 00:36:36,610
Jumpa lagi. Telefon aku kalau perlukan apa-apa.

437
00:37:21,647 --> 00:37:24,287
Buat kerja rumah muka surat 15.

438
00:37:25,681 --> 00:37:28,336
Dan, err...

439
00:37:29,115 --> 00:37:30,722
Rasanya cukup untuk hari ni.

440
00:37:32,256 --> 00:37:32,991
Jumpa lagi.

441
00:38:05,259 --> 00:38:06,090
P’Fah.

442
00:38:14,711 --> 00:38:16,303
Helo, P’Fah?

443
00:38:17,256 --> 00:38:17,971
Phoon.

444
00:38:18,204 --> 00:38:19,752
Asrama baru dah siap semua?

445
00:38:20,665 --> 00:38:22,034
Dah siap.

446
00:38:22,265 --> 00:38:23,641
Tiba-tiba hujan.

447
00:38:23,868 --> 00:38:25,863
Saya risau elektrik terputus, jadi saya telefon.

448
00:38:38,880 --> 00:38:39,762
Mm.

449
00:38:40,440 --> 00:38:41,743
Cuma hujan je.

450
00:38:46,103 --> 00:38:47,005
