485
00:40:49,345 --> 00:40:51,219
Nak apa-apa? Saya tolong pesan.

486
00:40:51,770 --> 00:40:53,029
Hmm.

487
00:40:53,299 --> 00:40:54,484
Saya nak latte ais.

488
00:40:54,585 --> 00:40:55,703
Baik.

489
00:41:00,637 --> 00:41:01,565
Satu latte ais, ya.

490
00:41:10,023 --> 00:41:11,456
Terima kasih.

491
00:41:12,351 --> 00:41:13,619
Ini dia.

492
