00:41:52,324 --> 00:41:54,659
Kau paling sesuai dengan senyuman.

503
00:41:54,958 --> 00:41:56,223
Senyum banyak-banyak, ya?

504
00:42:00,071 --> 00:42:01,025
Oh.

505
00:42:01,854 --> 00:42:04,192
Pasal tuisyen hari ni—

506
00:42:09,149 --> 00:42:09,934
Biar saya tengok.

507
00:42:33,924 --> 00:42:34,924
Macam mana nak buat ni?

508
00:42:34,968 --> 00:42:36,155
Okey, mari.

509
00:42:43,134 --> 00:42:45,574
Ha, yang ni. Baca soalan dulu, Phoon.

510
00:42:46,285 --> 00:42:50,642
Dia nak vektor unit sehala U, iaitu U.

511
00:42:50,877 --> 00:42:54,894
dan nilai mutlak U, mula-mula fikir—

512
00:42:55,080 --> 00:42:56,472
Apa itu vektor?

513
00:42:56,952 --> 00:42:58,444
Vektor ialah—

514
00:42:58,917 --> 00:43:01,130
Vektor datang daripada—

515
00:43:04,278 --> 00:43:05,315
Kau tengok apa?

516
00:43:07,048 --> 00:43:08,691
Kalau kau tak habiskan soalan ni,

517
00:43:09,977 --> 00:43:11,440
saya tak bagi kau balik.

518
00:43:51,515 --> 00:43:52,376
Phoon.

519
00:43:53,210 --> 00:43:54,174
Jom duduk sekejap.

520
00:44:43,345 --> 00:44:47,543
Depan tu menara jam. Datang kelas, kau nampak menara ni.

521
00:44:48,394 --> 00:44:49,785
Dan ni asrama.

522
00:44:52,263 --> 00:44:53,737
Kafeteria di sebelah kiri.

523
00:44:56,628 --> 00:44:57,404
Sebelah kiri.

524
00:45:02,391 --> 00:45:03,992
Itu kanan, Phoon.

525
00:45:34,709 --> 00:45:36,440
Saya ingat kau tak suka ambil gambar orang.

526
00:45:36,678 --> 00:45:38,592
Kenapa kebelakangan ni kau banyak ambil gambar saya?

527
00:45:40,309 --> 00:45:43,168
Saya nak simpan momen ni sebanyak mungkin.

528
00:45:45,567 --> 00:45:46,604
Dan gambar

529
00:45:47,451 --> 00:45:49,097
ialah bukti paling jelas.

530
00:45:52,595 --> 00:45:54,438
Macam kau suka ambil gambar Fun, kan?

531
00:46:39,831 --> 00:46:41,106
Masa kau dah habis.

532
00:46:44,616 --> 00:46:45,546
Saya tahu.

533
00:46:52,031 --> 00:46:53,770
Biar saya dengan P’Fah sekejap lagi.

534
00:46:54,115 --> 00:46:55,392
Sampai semester bermula.

535
00:46:58,666 --> 00:47:01,287
Lepas tu, saya takkan ganggu P’Fah lagi.

536
00:47:04,733 --> 00:47:06,592
Kalau terserempak di universiti?

537
00:47:07,914 --> 00:47:09,161
Saya buat macam tak nampak dia.

538
00:47:09,900 --> 00:47:11,644
Macam orang asing.

539
00:47:15,088 --> 00:47:16,842
Kalau Tonfah tak setuju?

540
00:47:19,084 --> 00:47:20,937
Saya akan buat dia benci saya.

541
00:47:23,302 --> 00:47:24,626
Sampai dia tak nak pandang saya pun.

542
00:47:27,029 --> 00:47:28,831
Pastikan kau buat macam kau cakap.

543
00:48:56,450 --> 00:48:58,041
P’Fah.

544
00:50:15,118 --> 00:50:17,980
Saya tak lapang hari ni. Batalkan tuisyen.

545
00:50:18,674 --> 00:50:21,149
Tak apa. Esok kau lapang?

546
00:50:27,703 --> 00:50:28,672
Tak.

547
00:50:30,028 --> 00:50:32,200
Jadi bila kau lapang?

548
00:50:39,041 --> 00:50:40,094
Saya dah tak lapang.

549
00:51:40,075 --> 00:51:41,020
Kau tak makan?

550
00:51:44,440 --> 00:51:45,515
Saya dah cakap, saya tak lapar.

551
00:51:50,134 --> 00:51:51,306
Tolong makan sikit.

552
00:51:54,945 --> 00:51:56,293
Saya kata saya tak makan.

553
00:52:01,820 --> 00:52:02,770
Maaf.

554
00:52:06,837 --> 00:52:08,392
Saya ada buat salah ke?

555
00:52:17,671 --> 00:52:18,428
Saya balik dulu.

556
00:52:20,502 --> 00:52:22,099
Macam mana kau nak balik?

557
00:52:24,514 --> 00:52:25,514
Saya panggil teksi.

558
00:52:37,616 --> 00:52:40,223
Selamat hari jadi, Johan!

559
00:52:40,414 --> 00:52:42,463
Habis! Hei, Fah!

560
00:52:46,746 --> 00:52:48,908
Semua!

561
00:52:49,226 --> 00:52:51,462
Hari ni hari jadi kawan aku, Johan.

562
00:52:52,841 --> 00:52:54,102
Teguk besar!

563
00:52:54,722 --> 00:52:56,444
Okey, sama-sama!

564
00:52:57,617 --> 00:53:00,106
Hei!

565
00:53:01,703 --> 00:53:04,768
Siapa habiskan gelas dapat duit!

566
00:53:06,068 --> 00:53:07,125
Mengarutlah kau.

567
00:53:07,311 --> 00:53:11,480
Dah, enjoy. Seronok sikit!

568
00:53:13,114 --> 00:53:14,795
Lagi seronok kalau kau tak ada.

569
00:53:17,405 --> 00:53:18,355
Hei!

570
00:53:18,485 --> 00:53:22,336
Okey, habiskan! Cheers!

571
00:53:22,475 --> 00:53:24,237
- Jomlah, Fah!
- Dari mana kau datang, lapar sangat?

572
00:53:24,528 --> 00:53:25,389
Fah!

573
00:53:26,730 --> 00:53:27,656
Fah!

574
00:53:30,800 --> 00:53:31,722
Hei, Fah!

575
00:53:33,539 --> 00:53:34,391
Apa?

576
00:53:34,518 --> 00:53:35,625
Kenapa dengan kau?

577
00:53:38,023 --> 00:53:39,848
Tak ada apa. Aku okey.

578
00:53:41,761 --> 00:53:43,914
Aku keluar kejap ambil angin.

579
00:53:48,629 --> 00:53:49,487
Kenapa dengan dia?

580
00:53:50,075 --> 00:53:52,506
- Apa masalah dia?
- Mana aku tahu?

581
00:54:03,016 --> 00:54:04,278
Hei, pergi cakap dengan dia.

582
00:54:07,149 --> 00:54:08,013
Habis rosak mood.

583
00:54:11,808 --> 00:54:12,634
Apa masalahnya?

584
00:54:19,746 --> 00:54:20,906
Ada benda kau nak cakap?

585
00:54:26,788 --> 00:54:27,949
Kau rasa aku okey?

586
00:54:29,037 --> 00:54:30,285
Maksud kau?

587
00:54:33,198 --> 00:54:34,194
Semua.

588
00:54:34,851 --> 00:54:35,991
Siapa diri aku.

589
00:54:36,814 --> 00:54:37,724
Perangai aku.

590
00:54:38,614 --> 00:54:40,047
Apa yang aku buat.

591
00:54:40,337 --> 00:54:41,520
Apa yang aku cakap.

592
00:54:42,555 --> 00:54:43,776
Ada apa-apa yang tak kena dengan aku?

593
00:54:45,595 --> 00:54:47,620
Apa yang buat kau hilang yakin macam ni?

594
00:54:53,293 --> 00:54:54,574
Adik aku.

595
00:54:56,358 --> 00:54:57,628
Adik kau?

596
00:54:59,385 --> 00:55:00,042
Ya.

597
00:55:01,613 --> 00:55:03,588
Budak sebelah rumah masa aku di Phuket.

598
00:55:05,432 --> 00:55:07,077
Kebetulan dia belajar di sini.

599
00:55:07,629 --> 00:55:09,478
Jadi kami terserempak semula.

600
00:55:11,143 --> 00:55:12,337
Dulu,

601
00:55:12,851 --> 00:55:14,031
kami rapat sangat.

602
00:55:15,340 --> 00:55:16,991
Dia orang yang aku tak boleh tak risaukan.

603
00:55:19,040 --> 00:55:22,185
Sampai aku nak jaga dia elok-elok.

604
00:55:23,970 --> 00:55:26,188
Tapi sejak aku keluar dari rumah,

605
00:55:27,148 --> 00:55:28,878
dan berhenti hubungi dia,

606
00:55:30,155 --> 00:55:31,533
aku rasa bersalah sampai sekarang.

607
00:55:34,432 --> 00:55:35,416
Dan sekarang,

608
00:55:36,284 --> 00:55:37,743
bila akhirnya kami jumpa semula,

609
00:55:38,546 --> 00:55:40,568
aku cuma nak tebus masa yang hilang.

610
00:55:41,785 --> 00:55:42,724
Tapi...

611
00:55:45,361 --> 00:55:46,709
Dia dah tak okey dengan kau?

612
00:55:50,905 --> 00:55:52,770
Mula-mula nampak okey.

613
00:55:53,628 --> 00:55:54,635
Tapi tiba-tiba,

614
00:55:54,805 --> 00:55:56,336
dia mula menjauh.

615
00:55:57,272 --> 00:55:58,739
Dia tak jawab panggilan aku.

616
00:55:59,065 --> 00:56:00,817
Dan jarang balas mesej aku.

617
00:56:01,988 --> 00:56:03,407
Macam dia dah tak nak jumpa aku.

618
00:56:05,777 --> 00:56:07,170
Jadi aku mula fikir yang

619
00:56:09,530 --> 00:56:11,207
mungkin lebih baik aku tak perlu ada.

620
00:56:14,275 --> 00:56:16,949
Masa kau tak ada, ada apa-apa jadi pada dia?

621
00:56:26,106 --> 00:56:27,308
Macam

622
00:56:27,567 --> 00:56:29,065
mak ayah dia dah bercerai.

623
00:56:29,998 --> 00:56:32,801
Tapi ayah dia dan kakak dia

624
00:56:33,400 --> 00:56:35,207
masih tinggal dengan dia macam dulu.

625
00:56:39,271 --> 00:56:40,745
Kau rasa dia sorok sesuatu daripada kau?

626
00:56:44,971 --> 00:56:45,961
Sorok sesuatu?

627
00:56:48,284 --> 00:56:49,078
Mungkin.

628
00:56:49,605 --> 00:56:50,878
Aku pun tak pasti.

629
00:56:51,888 --> 00:56:54,967
Aku cuma tahu dia dah rasa tak sedap hati pasal aku.

630
00:56:56,044 --> 00:56:57,811
Aku tak berani buat apa-apa, Hill.

631
00:56:58,148 --> 00:56:59,271
Rasa macam

632
00:56:59,557 --> 00:57:01,262
kalau aku tersilap sikit saja,

633
00:57:01,487 --> 00:57:03,040
aku akan hilang dia selamanya.

634
00:57:04,537 --> 00:57:05,890
Kau pasti

635
00:57:06,248 --> 00:57:07,339
dia cuma adik kau?

636
00:57:10,805 --> 00:57:11,973
Kenapa kau tanya macam tu?

637
00:57:16,311 --> 00:57:17,902
Dia nampak sangat penting bagi kau.

638
00:57:21,379 --> 00:57:23,936
Dia cuma adik aku.

639
00:57:24,878 --> 00:57:26,368
Aku jaga dia sejak kami kecil lagi.

640
00:57:26,531 --> 00:57:29,160
Jadi kau rasa itu tanggungjawab kau?

641
00:57:29,884 --> 00:57:30,669
Ya.

642
00:57:38,666 --> 00:57:39,594
Fah.

643
00:57:40,125 --> 00:57:41,525
Tentang apa yang kau tanya aku,

644
00:57:41,903 --> 00:57:43,333
ada apa-apa yang tak kena dengan kau,

645
00:57:44,610 --> 00:57:45,602
bagi aku,

646
00:57:46,142 --> 00:57:47,155
tak.

647
00:57:49,625 --> 00:57:51,520
Aku percaya kau dah buat yang terbaik.

648
00:57:54,131 --> 00:57:55,294
Kau asyik jaga orang lain.

649
00:57:56,497 --> 00:57:57,794
Cuba jaga diri kau juga.

650
00:58:02,266 --> 00:58:03,170
Terima kasih, Hill.

651
00:58:06,995 --> 00:58:08,310
Sekarang ni, aku pun

652
00:58:10,520 --> 00:58:11,804
mula rasa penat juga.

653
00:59:10,568 --> 00:59:11,423
Ayah.

654
00:59:13,080 --> 00:59:14,468
Aku tak nak buat semua ni lagi.

655
00:59:16,964 --> 00:59:18,377
Aku tak nak sakiti Abang Fah.

656
00:59:21,434 --> 00:59:24,128
Kalau tak nak, jangan tunjuk muka depan aku lagi.

657
00:59:31,891 --> 00:59:33,736
Tapi Abang Fah mesti dah benci aku.

658
00:59:34,754 --> 00:59:36,194
Lagi bagus macam tu.

659
00:59:36,955 --> 00:59:39,885
Jadi kau nak pilih siapa—Tonfah atau ayah kau?

660
00:59:47,543 --> 00:59:48,696
Ayah.

661
00:59:55,402 --> 00:59:57,128
Phoon boleh minta satu peluang?

662
00:59:59,091 --> 01:00:00,897
Cuma nak jumpa dia sekali lagi.

663
01:00:01,903 --> 01:00:03,945
Kau pasti itu kali terakhir?

664
01:00:14,811 --> 01:00:16,192
Ya, aku pasti.

665
01:00:18,465 --> 01:00:19,465
Lepas tu,

666
01:00:31,133 --> 01:00:33,247
aku takkan ada kaitan dengan Abang Fah lagi.

667
01:01:13,197 --> 01:01:13,973
Phoon.

668
01:01:17,180 --> 01:01:18,198
Kau tunggu lama?

669
01:01:20,293 --> 01:01:21,202
Tak lama pun.

670
01:01:25,071 --> 01:01:26,146
Kau tak sihat ke?

671
01:01:28,321 --> 01:01:29,405
Aku okey.

672
01:01:34,601 --> 01:01:35,722
Badan kau panas.

673
01:01:36,121 --> 01:01:37,869
Kenapa tak beritahu Abang Fah kalau kau tak sihat?

674
01:01:40,625 --> 01:01:41,577
Tak apa.

675
01:01:46,466 --> 01:01:49,183
Aku tak tahu bila aku mungkin dah lukakan kau tanpa sengaja.

676
01:01:49,684 --> 01:01:53,884
Kalau ada apa kau tak suka, boleh beritahu aku?

677
01:01:54,488 --> 01:01:56,020
Aku akan cuba perbaiki diri.

678
01:02:00,635 --> 01:02:01,971
Betul-betul tak apa.

679
01:02:03,213 --> 01:02:04,742
Kau okey macam kau sekarang.

680
01:02:08,687 --> 01:02:12,370
Jadi makan elok-elok, ya? Lepas tu makan ubat.

681
01:02:25,395 --> 01:02:27,017
Malam ni tidur di bilik Abang Fah.

682
01:02:30,706 --> 01:02:33,842
Kau sakit macam ni, aku tak boleh tinggal kau sorang.

683
01:02:34,817 --> 01:02:37,761
Atau Abang Fah tidur di bilik kau?

684
01:02:41,770 --> 01:02:43,377
Bilik kau okey.

685
01:02:45,037 --> 01:02:45,968
Okey.

686
01:03:16,262 --> 01:03:17,063
Ini ubat kau.

687
01:03:31,988 --> 01:03:32,955
Phoon.

688
01:03:33,272 --> 01:03:34,828
Nampak macam kau suka sangat kerusi ni.

689
01:03:39,722 --> 01:03:41,502
Boleh nampak langit di luar tingkap.

690
01:03:42,962 --> 01:03:44,471
Rasa tenang sangat.

691
01:03:59,888 --> 01:04:01,364
Badan kau masih panas.

692
01:04:01,841 --> 01:04:02,988
Nak baring dan rehat?

693
01:04:13,081 --> 01:04:14,905
Aku duduk sini baca dekat sebelah kau.

694
01:04:15,420 --> 01:04:17,074
Kalau kau tak okey, panggil aku.

695
01:04:17,937 --> 01:04:18,909
Okey.

696
01:04:33,075 --> 01:04:34,891
Ini mungkin kali terakhir

697
01:04:35,531 --> 01:04:37,585
aku dapat bersama Abang Fah macam ni.

698
01:05:12,232 --> 01:05:13,632
Kali terakhir.

699
01:05:14,226 --> 01:05:15,856
Kali terakhir yang aku harap takkan datang.

700
01:05:39,697 --> 01:05:41,198
Selamat tinggal.

701
01:06:33,638 --> 01:06:34,580
Abang Fah.

702
01:06:40,722 --> 01:06:41,684
Phoon.

703
01:06:42,688 --> 01:06:43,635
Phoon.

704
01:06:43,949 --> 01:06:45,161
Kau dalam, kan?

705
01:06:45,493 --> 01:06:47,114
Keluar jumpa aku sekejap.

706
01:06:48,248 --> 01:06:49,121
Phoon.

707
01:06:50,503 --> 01:06:51,782
Kau okey?

708
01:06:51,986 --> 01:06:53,365
Keluar dan cakap dengan aku, tolong.

709
01:06:54,644 --> 01:06:55,562
Phoon.

710
01:06:59,837 --> 01:07:00,681
Phoon.

711
01:07:01,462 --> 01:07:03,386
Aku tahu kau ada dalam.

712
01:07:03,511 --> 01:07:05,019
Kau tak nak jawab aku?

713
01:07:09,776 --> 01:07:11,188
Kau benci aku sekarang?

714
01:07:16,216 --> 01:07:19,045
Aku betul-betul tak tahu apa salah aku.

715
01:07:20,441 --> 01:07:22,032
Tapi boleh kau beritahu aku,

716
01:07:22,291 --> 01:07:23,768
apa salah aku?

717
01:07:31,351 --> 01:07:33,413
Kau adik aku yang penting.

718
01:07:35,122 --> 01:07:36,915
Boleh tak kita kembali macam dulu?

719
01:07:50,931 --> 01:07:52,035
Pergi.

720
01:07:54,685 --> 01:07:56,282
Merepek apa kau ni?

721
01:07:57,488 --> 01:07:58,743
Menyampah.

722
01:08:00,377 --> 01:08:01,358
Kau sedar tak,

723
01:08:01,859 --> 01:08:04,109
betapa menyampahnya kau?

724
01:08:04,691 --> 01:08:06,302
Dan jauhkan diri dari pintu aku.

725
01:08:06,997 --> 01:08:08,020
Pergi mana kau suka.

726
01:08:17,435 --> 01:08:18,601
Maaf.

727
01:08:19,380 --> 01:08:20,622
Aku pergi sekarang.

728
01:08:48,856 --> 01:08:50,217
Maaf.

729
01:08:55,214 --> 01:08:56,783
Aku betul-betul minta maaf.

730
01:09:11,385 --> 01:09:13,755
Aku tak pernah nak semua ni jadi.

731
01:09:24,994 --> 01:09:27,234
Dah dihantar sejak kau kecil lagi.

732
01:09:27,391 --> 01:09:30,562
Sejak umur kau setahun, setiap bulan Mac.

733
01:09:30,816 --> 01:09:32,002
Bulan hari jadi kau.

734
01:09:32,152 --> 01:09:33,296
Mak?

735
01:09:33,380 --> 01:09:34,688
Ada apa?

736
01:09:34,948 --> 01:09:36,420
Kalau nak tahu, pindahkan duit dulu.

737
01:09:36,647 --> 01:09:37,644
Pergi ambil di rumah.

738
01:09:37,940 --> 01:09:41,465
Aku ada idea—macam mana nak buat Maew cakap dengan P'Fah.

739
01:09:41,601 --> 01:09:43,625
- Kenapa susu coklat?
- Sebab aku suka.

740
01:09:43,776 --> 01:09:44,728
Kita boleh je beli semua, tahu.

741
01:09:44,801 --> 01:09:46,610
Wah, baiknya ada orang.

742
01:09:46,709 --> 01:09:48,296
Aku rasa P'Fah tak suka itu.

743
01:09:50,962 --> 01:09:53,063
Tengok Fah—kuat cemburu.

